<i>adverb</i>: 허술히 [허술히], 소홀히 [소홀히], 무심히 [무심히], 등한히 [등ː한히], 냉정히 [냉ː정히], 냉랭히 [냉ː냉히], 냉담히 [냉ː담히], 가만히 [가만히], 가만 [가만] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>허술히 [허술히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shabbily; humbly</dd><br>
<dd>낡고 헐어서 보잘것없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being old and worn out, making it look worthless.</dd><br>
<dd>2. loosely; laxly; poorly</dd><br>
<dd>꼼꼼하지 못하고 빈틈이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of showing a loophole without being meticulous.</dd><br>
<dd>3. indifferently; inattentively; negligently</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 행동이 무심하고 소홀하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of looking or acting indifferent or paying little attention to something.</dd><br>
<dt>소홀히 [소홀히]</dt><br>
<dd>indifferently; negligently</dd><br>
<dd>중요하게 생각하지 않아 주의나 정성이 부족하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With insufficient care or caution about something because one does not think it is important.</dd><br>
<dt>무심히 [무심히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. heedlessly</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 생각이나 감정이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without thought or emotion.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indifferently</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 사람에 대하여 걱정하는 마음이나 관심이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without care or concern towards a matter or person.</dd><br>
<dt>등한히 [등ː한히]</dt><br>
<dd>negligently; indifferently; with indifference</dd><br>
<dd>무엇에 관심이 없거나 소홀하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of having no interest in or being careless about something.</dd><br>
<dt>냉정히 [냉ː정히]</dt><br>
<dd>coldly; callously; indifferently</dd><br>
<dd>따뜻한 정이 없고 차가운 태도로.</dd><br>
<dd>Without kindness and with a cold attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>냉랭히 [냉ː냉히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. coldly</dd><br>
<dd>온도가 낮아서 차게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being icy due to a low temperature.</dd><br>
<dd>2. coldly; callously; indifferently</dd><br>
<dd>태도 등이 다정하지 않고 차갑게.</dd><br>
<dd>With an attitude, etc., that is cold, not kind.</dd><br>
<dt>냉담히 [냉ː담히]</dt><br>
<dd>indifferently; coldly</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 마음씨 등이 무관심하고 쌀쌀맞게.</dd><br>
<dd>With an indifferent and cold attitude or mind.</dd><br>
<dt>가만히 [가만히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quietly; motionlessly</dd><br>
<dd>움직이지 않거나 말 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without movement or words.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indifferently</dd><br>
<dd>일을 해결하기 위한 어떠한 대책이나 노력 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without any action or effort to solve something.</dd><br>
<dd>3. deliberatey; carefully</dd><br>
<dd>마음을 차분하게 하고 주의를 기울여.</dd><br>
<dd>With calm and care.</dd><br>
<dd>4. silently</dd><br>
<dd>남이 모르게 조용히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others will not notice.</dd><br>
<dt>가만 [가만]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quietly; motionlessly</dd><br>
<dd>움직이지 않거나 말 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without movement or words.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indifferently</dd><br>
<dd>일을 해결하기 위한 어떠한 대책이나 노력 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without any action or effort to solve something.</dd><br>
<dd>3. deliberately; carefully</dd><br>
<dd>마음을 차분하게 하고 주의를 기울여.</dd><br>
<dd>With calm and care.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>